text: Product Composition:        MyCrewDoses products consist of 100% mushroom extracts, specifically the fruiting bodies, excluding mycelium (mushroom root system) or grain additives.    Supplier Information:        Our extracts are sourced from Nammex, a supplier with over 40 years of experience in organic mushroom cultivation. Nammex extracts are from certified organic mushrooms, grown or wildcrafted in China.    Quality Control:        Extracts undergo rigorous quality control, including two rounds of testing for heavy metals, agricultural chemicals, and microbial contamination, adhering to dietary supplement standards.    Cultivation and Origin:        The majority of mushrooms for supplements are grown in China, accounting for over 85% of global supply. China's history of mushroom cultivation dates back to the early 1200s, making it a leading source for organic mushroom extracts.    Comparison with U.S. Products:        U.S. products typically use mycelium grown on grains, resulting in high grain content and low active compounds. Our products differ by using actual mushrooms and being tested for beta-glucans and starch.    Mushroom vs. Myceliated Grain:        Myceliated grain is a low-cost method producing high-starch, grain-based mycelium products, unlike our products which are pure mushroom extracts. Indicators of myceliated grain include terms like mycelium, myceliated brown rice, and similar phrases on product labels.    Growing Medium:        Most medicinal mushrooms are grown on sawdust, a byproduct from sawmills, with reishi as an exception, grown on hardwood logs.    Heavy Metals Testing:        Products are screened for heavy metals twice, following American Herbal Products Association guidelines, with stricter limits based on our recommended dosage.    Extraction Process:        Mushrooms are dried, ground, and cooked multiple times with water or alcohol to break down cell walls and extract beneficial compounds. The final product is a concentrated, dried powder without water or alcohol.    Active Compounds:    MyCrewDoses products contain 5-10 times more beta-glucans compared to mycelium on grain products.
